quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,73,"Twanabagize abayobozi bayobora ku bw’itegeko ryacu, tunabahishurira (ko bagomba) gukora ibyiza, guhozaho amasengesho no gutanga amaturo.Kandi ni twe (Allah, twenyine) basengaga"
  21,74,"Na Lutwi (Loti) twamuhaye ubushishozi mu guca imanza tunamuha ubumenyi, ndetse turamurokora tumukura mu mudugudu (wa Sodoma) wakoraga ibibi. Mu by’ukuri, (abari bawutuye) bari abantu babi bakaba n’ibyigomeke"
  21,75,"Twanamushyize mu mpuhwe zacu. Mu by’ukuri,umwe yari mu ntungane"
  21,76,"Kandi (wibuke yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Nuhu yatakambaga mbere. Twakiriye ubusabe bwe,tumurokorana n’abantu be mu makuba ahambaye"
  21,77,"Twanamukijije abantu bahakanye ibimenyetso byacu. Mu by’ukuri, bari abantu babi maze tubaroha (mu mazi) bose uko bakabaye"
  21,78,Kandi (wibuke) Dawudi na Sulayimani igihe bacaga urubanza rw’umurima wari wonwe n’intamaza bamwe mu bantu mu ijoro. Kandi twari abahamya b’uburyo barukijije
  21,79,"Nuko dushoboza Sulayimani kurusobanukirwa neza; kandi bombi (Dawudi na Sulayimani) twabahaye ubushishozi n’ubumenyi. Twategetse imisozi n’inyoni guca bugufi kugira ngo bijye bisingiza (Allah, bifatanyije) na Dawudi. Kandi byose ni twe twabikoze"
  21,80,Twanamwigishije kubacurira ingabo kugira ngo zibarinde ku rugamba. Ese mujya mushimira
  21,81,"Kandi twategetse umuyaga (kumvira) Sulayimani(ukajya umutwara) ku bw’itegekorye, umujyana mu gihugu (cya Shami) twahundagajemo imigisha. Kandi ibintu byose twari tubizi"